text: Asked able to choose and replied “yes”. Requested 1 wing, 1 rib and 1 tight…. but need to add $2. The menu 3 pieces size are almost the same from what I requested and selling at $8.50. Daylight robber. Horrible stall and will never visit.
Order take away fries, th fries is like fry don’t know how many time alrdy.
Amazed by their chicken wing quality and taste during the first visit. Tried chicken wing spaghetti during 2nd visit and it also taste good.  Service is good as well. Recommended!

Ordered the beef steak but was shock at the size and thickness of the beef steak. Its not worth the value of $11.90, I can get a decent 200gram beef steak at Char Grill for just $10.90. This is my first and will be my last to patronise this stall.

Fries are over cooked, all are in dark brown colour and super hard to eat. Very disappointed in the food that they serve now, standard is not like before and the price is not cheap as a hawker western in the first place. Not going back ever.
